    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, currently offered in showroom condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior environment that remains in pristine, original state. Every mechanical and aesthetic component has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our exacting standards for excellence. For the discerning enthusiast who demands an unparalleled ownership experience, this vehicle stands as a testament to meticulous care and superior quality.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
