      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute gem to believe it! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s honestly in showroom condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. There isn't a single blemish on it, and the interior is just spotless. I\u2019m looking for a good home for my pride and joy, so if you want a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, let\u2019s chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 1997 Acura Integra Type R in museum-grade condition. This DC2 features the high-revving B18C5 heart, distinguished by its hand-polished intake ports and lightened valvetrain, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The close-ratio 5-speed manual gearbox shifts flawlessly, paired with the factory-spec helical limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Chassis rigidity is maintained via original factory-installed bracing, and the suspension retains its specific Type R geometry and damping rates. This is a numbers-matching example with all original VIN tags intact, free of any aftermarket modifications or mechanical fatigue. A definitive analog masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Pristine condition. Garage kept. Single owner. No mechanical issues. Clean title. Service records available.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
