    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was purchased. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, having been professionally ceramic coated and stored in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained exclusively by certified technicians with a comprehensive folder of service records included. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the advanced infotainment system, functions flawlessly. With exceptionally low mileage and recent preventative maintenance\u2014including a full fluid flush and brand-new performance tires\u2014it drives with the precision and smoothness of a brand-new vehicle. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated machine for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
